Springseed is a simply awesome way to take notes. We hope you enjoy using it as much as we did creating it. It's only going to get better.

### Features:

- Dropbox Sync
- Markdown Support
- A Beautiful, Easy Interface
- Sort your tasks with Notebooks
- Easily search through your notes
- Free & Open Source

Springseed is free and open source software under the [BSD License.](http://opensource.org/licenses/BSD-2-Clause) This means you're free to distribute Springseed to others, free of charge. If you would love to see something in Springseed, you can make the contribution, if you wish.

Show your support for Springseed by suggesting a feature or reporting a bug at our [GitHub page](http://github.com/consindo/notes). [Donations](http://springseed.com/donate) are also appreciated.

We've got a lot planned for Springseed - join us on our journey!